segments.text: Happy Halloween!
Yeah, I love Halloween.
Me too.
I'm a Christmas girl.
It's alright.
Nerissa!
You never sent me that picture of you in your costume.
Oh, I ended up feeling sick so I ended up not changing and dressing up after all.
It was really depressing for me.
I know, I wanted to die.
You can dress up sick.
Yeah, you can always dress up.
But now I'm looking for like...
I want to find a cute dress to wear for Christmas.
Did she just go naked?
No, you can't go naked, it's Christmas!
Yeah, it'll be like a Christmas present!
No!
Like, Merry Christmas, put a ribbon around your body.
That's like some fancy lingerie type.
You guys are sick. You're sick.
Well, yeah, I am sick actually.
